_sText: I saw this map 4 months ago and I'm trying to save ZoiDiCabra's attempt to recreate CSGO's Vertigo since it was a good idea but he left his project since the day I saw it. I fixed a lot of FPS issues throughout the entire map, decreased the height of the building causing rendering issues that leads to game crash, fixed model brushes and hint-skips combination to suddenly increase the FPS, removed unnecessary crane model at Ramp that dramatically decreases FPS and changed it to a simple block one. Credits to him and to his map attempt. Hand-tuned NAV and new skybox (militia_hdr)
